<P><LINE><BOLD>THE SQUAMISH NATION (ALSO KNOWN AS THE SQUAMISH INDIAN BAND) AND X&Ag;LEK/SEKY&Ua; SIYAM, CHIEF IAN CAMPBELL IN HIS OWN BEHALF AND ON BEHALF OF ALL MEMBERS OF THE SQUAMISH NATION</BOLD></LINE></P>
